edu.xtec.jclic.bags

Class ActivityBagElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.xtec.jclic.bags.ActivityBagElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Editable, Cloneable

    public class ActivityBagElement
extends Object
implements Editable, Cloneable
    This class stores a XML Element that defines an Activity. It stores also a HashMap with references of other objects to this activity, and implements some useful methods to directly retrieve some properites of the related Activity, like its name. ActivityBagElements are usually stored into ActivityBag objects.
